  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may use your destructive blast to shield a target within range from ranged weapons, area effects, or even other destructive blasts for 1 round, giving them the benefits of evasion, a +2 cover bonus to AC vs. ranged attacks, and a +1 cover bonus to their Reflex saves. These bonuses increase by +2/+1 respectively for every 5 caster levels you possess.</p>\n<p>By spending a spell point, you may perform a rebuff as an immediate action, or provide the benefits to all targets within 10-foot of you + 5 feet per 5 caster levels. You may spend 2 spell points to gain both of these benefits with the same rebuff.</p>\n",
